Package org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.groups.artists

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtistDetailsController
    Represents a controller that handle an artist's details; shows and let them to be saved to the disk.
    ArtistsController
    Represents a controller that aggregate a list of songs by their artist tag.
    ArtistsController.ArtistSongsGroupController
    Controller that handles the songs list of a group just like SongsGroupSongsController that furthermore allow to switch between the song list and the artist's details and save those to the disk.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ArtistsController.ArtistSongsGroupController.PaneMode
    Types of pane that can be embedded in this controller.
